
Instructions for running the application:
	folder for images: images;
	folder for data: data.

BONUSES:
		1) restarting the game;
		2) save the modified decision tree to an XML file for the 
		next game.


NEW JAVA CLASS: JOptionPane.
JOptionPane creates standard dialogs. I use it to show the
user a list of restaurants, ask the user to think of one of them, let the 
user pick a restaurant that is not on the pre-specified list, etc. 
Link: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/components/dialog.htm